{
  "stem": "812.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I had said earlier, life was fairly comfortable in Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to remember that I never knew anything other than camp life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was four years old when we left Germany, and almost immediately, were incarcerated, almost immediate, were in some sort of a camp situation.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And for me, and I believe also for my brother, it was quite comfortable being in Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I made friends.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were many, many children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had some sort of education.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was quite primitive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But groups would get together with teachers who would teach us preliminary lessons-- arithmetic, German at that time-- even though we were in Holland, it was German that we were taught, because we were with German-speaking people.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] we-- we, as children, didn't feel the discomfort nearly as did the adults.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we didn't feel as threatened as the adults, because, as I said, we never knew anything different.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] As far as toys and games, there was nothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I did have one little rag doll that I always had with me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We made up our own games.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I remember that I [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] made believe-- I always want a little puppy or something of my own.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I remember, in the summer time, or when the sun would shine, I had a little mirror with me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And with the reflection of the mirror on the ground would be my puppy and my pets.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I would walk along, and always looking back at him and making believe that he was real.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we also had-- would save certain pieces of-- of wrapping paper that we would find or we would get.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we would smoothen it with our nails, and we would save that.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
